---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { SOCIAL } from "../config";
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="A software engineer in Seattle. Here is the longer version."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="kicker">About</p>
    <h1>The longer <em>version</em>.</h1>
  </section>

  <div class="bio">
    <p>
      I am an SDE at Amazon in Seattle. My day-to-day is
      Java, some TypeScript, a lot of CloudWatch. The work is mostly
      about moving data between places without losing anything along
      the way. It is less glamorous than it sounds and more interesting
      than it looks.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before Amazon I was in India for a few years. I started at Nucleus
      Software writing Java for a bank's loan processing module - my
      first real job and my first real production outage. Then I moved
      to Deloitte working on the Salesforce side, mostly admin and Apex.
      After that I came to the US for my masters at the University at
      Buffalo. Grew up before that in Hyderabad and a smaller town
      called Thorrur.
    </p>
    <p>
      On the side I build small things. The one I am most proud of is
      a movie app that does recommendations locally using embeddings -
      no OpenAI, no API bill. Also a vocabulary RPG that turns looking
      up words while reading into something slightly less boring. I
      read more than I probably should and I keep picking side projects
      that let me learn exactly one new thing at a time.
    </p>
  </div>

  <section class="links-section">
    <h2>Links</h2>
    <ul class="links">
      <li><span class="label">Email</span> <a href={SOCIAL.email}>{SOCIAL.email.replace("mailto:", "")}</a></li>
      <li><span class="label">GitHub</span> <a href={SOCIAL.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{SOCIAL.github.replace(/^https?:\/\//, "")}</a></li>
      <li><span class="label">LinkedIn</span> <a href={SOCIAL.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{SOCIAL.linkedin.replace(/^https?:\/\//, "")}</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .hero {
    margin: 1.5rem 0 4rem 0;
  }
  .kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 0.95;
    margin: 0;
  }
  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .bio {
    max-width: 38rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .bio p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
  }
  .bio p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .links-section {
    max-width: 38rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .links-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
  }
  .links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .links li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 5.5rem 1fr;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .label {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
</style>
